  <description>Learn more about the Culturally Responsive Bystander Intervention (CuRB) trainings, which explore how identity, privilege and power impact how we support those around us experiencing power-based interpersonal violence. CuRB helps participants practice strategies, skills and tools to be an active bystander</description>
